<p>
	Goloka incense is a hand rolled traditional incense and contains only the finest organic ingredients and no animal products. Goloka incense products support the Akshaya Patra Foundation, a charitable organisation that provides meals for Indian children in poor areas and ensures they are able to get a full education. Without this support many children would be forced to beg on the streets in order to be fed. By buying Goloka incense products you are improving the life of over 500,000 children.&nbsp;</p>
<p>
	Goloka have been creating quality incense for over 16 years, and part of their proceeds are given to charitable causes that help provide meals for underprivileged children and providing vocational training and scholarships.</p>